WHY DO YOU NEED THIS?

IN THE VAULT FOR AUGUST 2024:

PIGMENTS PRESETS

The Pigments presets this month include a playful bass sequence, an ambient synth pad, a glassy lead synth and more!

OMNISPHERE PRESETS

This month’s Omnisphere presets include a breathy arpeggiated sequence, a fragile digital pad, an atmospheric texture and more!

U-he Repro-1 PRESETS

This month you’ll find 5 presets for U-he Repro-1. These presets include a delicate triangle arpeg, an aggressive mono key, a sharp lead and more!

GForce Oberheim SEM PRESETS

The Wildcard synth for August is… GForce Oberheim SEM! This powerful little mono synth is beautifully simply, yet carries a huge sound! You’ll find a punchy bass synth, a sweeping arpeg and more!

TOTAL COLLECTION:

– 750 PRESETS –
